data.description: Immaculately maintained 3 bedroom home plus a study. Kitchen with granite countertops, walk in pantry, breakfast bar, built in hutch, 42 inch cabinets, tile backsplash, flat burner range and microwave. Master with window seat has ensuite bath with garden tub, separate shower, double vanities and walk in closet with built ins. Other features include rounded corners, covered patio, breakfast area window seat, 2 inch blinds, formal dining window seat, split bedroom plan, woodburning fireplace in family room, linen closet, cabinets in utility room, oversized garage, sprinklers, security system, Ecobee thermostat, wood fenced yard and more. Seller can not close before November 7, 2023
